  "Discovery and competency map": "调研与能力图谱",
  "We sit with you to understand the learner, the sector and the standard. From this we draw a single competency map that holds the rest of the programme together.": "我们与您共同探讨，理解学员、行业与标准。在此基础上，我们绘制一张统一的能力图谱，将整个课程的其余部分串联起来。",
  "Step II": "第二步",
  "Course Proposal and course materials": "课程提案与课程材料",
  "We draft the Course Proposal (CP) Form, lesson and assessment plans, trainer guide and learner materials, all version-controlled and submission-ready.": "我们拟写课程提案（CP）表格、课程与评估计划、培训师指南及学员材料，全部进行版本控制并可随时提交。",
