  "Pairing adult educators and evidence": "匹配成人教育工作者并准备佐证",
  "Where required, we pair the course with adult educators who meet the SSG AE Qualifications and are registered on the National AE Registry, and prepare the supporting evidence.": "在需要时，我们为课程匹配符合 SSG AE 资格并已在国家 AE 注册名册（National AE Registry）登记的成人教育工作者，并准备佐证材料。",
  "Step IV": "第四步",
