  "Part one": "第一部分",
  "National AE Registry": "国家 AE 注册名册",
  "Adult educators assigned to the course must be registered with the National Adult Educator Registry, managed by the Institute for Adult Learning at the Singapore University of Social Sciences.": "分配至该课程的成人教育工作者必须在国家成人教育工作者注册名册（National Adult Educator Registry）登记，该名册由新加坡社会科学大学（Singapore University of Social Sciences）的成人学习研究院（Institute for Adult Learning）管理。",
