  "WSQ ACTA or ACLP": "WSQ ACTA 或 ACLP",
  "Each AE who trains or assesses must hold the WSQ Advanced Certificate in Training and Assessment, the WSQ Advanced Certificate in Learning and Performance (ACLP 2.0), or an equivalent recognised by SSG at its sole discretion.": "每位进行培训或评估的 AE 必须持有 WSQ 培训与评估高级证书（WSQ Advanced Certificate in Training and Assessment）、WSQ 学习与绩效高级证书（WSQ Advanced Certificate in Learning and Performance，ACLP 2.0），或由 SSG 全权酌情认可的同等资格。",
