  "Keith Ho": "Keith Ho",
  "Founder · Curriculum Developer In House Legal Counsel": "创办人 · 课程开发者 内部法律顾问",
  "Bachelor of Laws (Hons) (UK) SDip (HRM), MSHRI DACE, ACLP, ACTA, IAL-SAE TAEPP Level 3 Senior Professional AE HRD Corp Accredited Trainer (Msia) Verify TAEPP ↗": "法学学士（荣誉）（英国） SDip (HRM), MSHRI DACE, ACLP, ACTA, IAL-SAE TAEPP 第三级高级专业 AE HRD Corp 认证培训师（马来西亚） 验证 TAEPP ↗",
  "keith.ho@2birds.asia": "keith.ho@2birds.asia",
  "Keith Ho is a training and education professional with more than a decade in the Training and Adult Education sector. He serves as General Manager of 1ST Aid and Healthcare Pte. Ltd. and runs 2birds, an independent advisory and course development practice.": "Keith Ho 是一位培训与教育专才，在培训及成人教育领域拥有逾十年经验。他担任 1ST Aid and Healthcare Pte. Ltd. 的总经理，并经营 2birds——一所独立的咨询及课程开发事务所。",
  "He holds a Bachelor of Laws (Hons) from Birmingham City University, an Allied Certificate in Legal Skills from Temasek Polytechnic, a Specialist Diploma in Human Resource Management from Nanyang Polytechnic, a Diploma in Adult and Continuing Education (DACE) and an Advanced Certificate in Training and Assessment (ACTA) from the Institute for Adult Learning. He is a recognised IAL Specialist Adult Educator, a member of the Singapore Human Resources Institute (MSHRI) and a HRD Corp certified trainer in Malaysia.": "他持有 Birmingham City University 的法学学士（荣誉）学位、Temasek Polytechnic 的法律技能辅修证书、Nanyang Polytechnic 的人力资源管理专科文凭，以及 Institute for Adult Learning 颁授的成人及持续教育文凭（DACE）和培训与评估高级证书（ACTA）。他是经认可的 IAL 专业成人教育工作者、新加坡人力资源学院会员（MSHRI），以及马来西亚的 HRD Corp 认证培训师。",
  "His career has spanned the Singapore Productivity Centre, the Institute of Singapore Chartered Accountants and Adept Academy. At SGPC, he developed courses including the Fair Tenancy Industry Committee programme, which The Business Times featured in 2022 for promoting the Fair Tenancy Code of Conduct between landlords and tenants. At Adept Academy, he contributed to curriculum development and training innovation and achieved a Grade 1 outcome under SSG's Training Provider Quality Assurance framework. In 2025, SSG invited him as a speaker to share best practices with the training provider community.": "他的职业生涯横跨 Singapore Productivity Centre、Institute of Singapore Chartered Accountants 及 Adept Academy。在 SGPC，他开发了多门课程，包括 Fair Tenancy Industry Committee 项目，该项目因推广业主与租户之间的 Fair Tenancy Code of Conduct，于 2022 年获 The Business Times 专题报道。在 Adept Academy，他参与课程开发与培训创新，并在 SSG 的培训机构质量保证框架下取得第一级（Grade 1）成绩。2025 年，SSG 邀请他作为讲者，向培训机构社群分享最佳实践。",
  "He works within SSG frameworks including WSQ and CASL, and has facilitated training delivery and courseware development for the Singapore Furniture Industries Council Institute, Xprienz, Carrie Academy International, Focus Learning Centre, QD Academy, Addison Institute and HY M&E Consultancy, covering artificial intelligence, healthcare, human resources, legal, leadership, food safety, built environment, data science, supply chain and digital analytics.": "他在 SSG 框架（包括 WSQ 与 CASL）下开展工作，并曾为 Singapore Furniture Industries Council Institute、Xprienz、Carrie Academy International、Focus Learning Centre、QD Academy、Addison Institute 及 HY M&E Consultancy 提供培训实施与课程开发支持，涵盖人工智能、医疗保健、人力资源、法律、领导力、食品安全、建筑环境、数据科学、供应链及数字分析等领域。",
  "Correspondence with Keith is welcome by email at keith.ho@2birds.asia.": "欢迎通过电子邮件 keith.ho@2birds.asia 与 Keith 联系。",
