  "Write to us, and we will write back.": "来信予我们，我们必将回复。",
  "If you are a certified adult educator or a subject matter expert with standing in your sector, leave us a short note. We read every submission and reply within five working days. There is no fee, no obligation, and no exclusivity.": "若您是经认证的成人教育工作者，或在所属行业中享有声望的领域专家，请给我们留下简短的讯息。我们会阅读每一份提交，并在五个工作日内回复。无须费用，无任何义务，亦无排他性。",
  "I. All information is held in confidence and used only to assess fit.": "I. 所有信息均予以保密，仅用于评估匹配度。",
  "II. Joining the community is by invitation; submission is not acceptance.": "II. 加入社群须经邀请；提交并不等同于获接纳。",
