  /* ---- home: hero & belief ---- */
  "The growing community": "不断壮大的社群",
  "By Practitioners, not consultants.": "由从业者执笔，而非顾问。",
  "A practice of curriculum developers, subject-matter experts andadult educators, trusted by Approved Training Organisations (ATOs).We take only a handful of engagements each quarter, so that each one has our undivided attention. Every one begins on a blank page, written for the situation in front of us. We keep no templates, and we reuse nothing.":
    "由课程开发者、领域专家与成人教育工作者组成的事务所，深受认可培训机构（ATO）信赖。我们每季度只承接少数委托，以确保每一项都获得我们全心的投入。每一项都从一张白纸开始，为眼前的实际情况量身而作。我们不套用模板，亦不重复使用任何既有内容。",
  "What we believe": "我们的信念",
  "Learning ought not to be priced out of reach of the people who most need to learn. The practice keeps its costs deliberately modest so the fees never find their way down to the learner.":
    "学习不应因价格高昂而将最需要学习的人拒之门外。本所刻意将成本维持在适度水平，使费用永不会转嫁到学员身上。",

  /* ---- home: heritage ---- */
  "Our practice · our standing": "本所 · 我们的立场",
  "A short heritage, plainly stated.": "简短的沿革，如实陈述。",
  "Four markers from the practice's correspondence, the milestones we feel comfortable putting on paper, and which a curious reader might want to weigh before writing to us.":
    "源自本所往来记录的四个标记，是我们乐于落笔记载的里程碑，也是有意垂询者在致函之前或许愿意权衡的依据。",
  "The practice opens by invitation, the beginning of a growing community of curriculum developers and adult educators.":
    "本所以邀请制开张，是一个不断壮大的课程开发者与成人教育工作者社群的起点。",
  "The practice has rendered curriculum and advisory services across thirteen Approved Training Organisations, spanning multiple sectors and sectorial frameworks.":
    "本所已为十三家认可培训机构提供课程与顾问服务，涵盖多个行业及行业框架。",
  "Approaching one hundred courseware submissions completed collectively across the practice, spanning WSQ and non-WSQ certifiable courses.":
    "本所累计完成近百份课件呈交，涵盖 WSQ 与非 WSQ 可认证课程。",
  "Courseware reaches the industry at scale, including the FTIC Code of Conduct workshop reported byThe Business Times in 2022.":
    "课件已大规模惠及业界，包括 2022 年获《The Business Times》报道的 FTIC 行为守则工作坊。",

  /* ---- home: services ---- */
  "Fields of expertise": "专业领域",
  "Four practice areas,one standard of care.": "四大业务领域，同一份用心标准。",
  "On engagement": "关于委托",
  "Whenever it suits you, allow us to prepare an indicative figure. Our plans are tiered, sized to your scope, and ease with each further curriculum we develop.":
    "在您方便之时，容我们为您拟备一份指示性报价。我们的方案分级设定，按您的范围量身而定，并随每开发一门新课程而递减。",
  "Curriculum Development": "课程开发",
  "Courses mapped to the Skills Framework, written for the room and ready for courseware submission.":
    "课程对接技能框架（Skills Framework），为课堂而写，可直接用于课件呈交。",
  "We map every course first, to the technical and critical core skills of the relevant Skills Framework, or to the Course Approval Skills List where it sits outside WSQ. From that map we design the rest, the curriculum and lesson plans, the assessment plan and instruments, the trainer and learner guides. We submit the course on TPGateway on your behalf, and stay with it through SSG's queries until it is approved.":
    "我们首先将每一门课程对接至相关技能框架的技术核心技能与关键核心技能；若课程不属于 WSQ，则对接至课程审批技能清单（CASL）。在此对接的基础上，我们设计其余一切——课程与教案、评估方案与工具、培训师与学员指南。我们代您在 TPGateway 上呈交课程，并全程跟进 SSG 的提问，直至获得批准。",
  "Non-WSQ / WSQ courses": "非 WSQ / WSQ 课程",
  "CASL": "CASL",
  "TPGateway submission": "TPGateway 呈交",
  "Sourcing and ATO Setup": "人才招募与机构设立",
  "The people and the registration, from the first conversation to your first cohort.":
    "从第一次洽谈到您的第一批学员，为您安排人才与完成注册。",
  "We introduce trainers and subject-matter experts to you at no cost, and accompany prospective and first-time training organisations through the whole of setup. From registration and accreditation to the moment your first cohort sits down.":
    "我们免费为您引荐培训师与领域专家，并全程陪伴有意进入及首次设立的培训机构完成整个设立流程——从注册与认证，直至您的第一批学员正式入座。",
  "Trainer and SME sourcing": "培训师与领域专家招募",
  "ATO / OR registration": "ATO / OR 注册",
  "Academic operations": "教务运营",
  "TPQA and Compliance Advisory": "TPQA 与合规顾问",
  "Ready for the audit, long before the date is set.": "在审核日期确定之前，早已万事俱备。",
  "It begins with a complimentary consultation on your TPQA and CQC standing, with a pre-audit gap analysis against SSG's criteria. We close the gaps, strengthen the operation where it needs it, and leave the documents in order and the work behind them already done.":
    "首先就您的 TPQA 与 CQC 状况提供免费咨询，并依据 SSG 的标准进行审核前差距分析。我们弥合差距，在需要之处强化运营，使文件井然有序，且其背后的工作早已完成。",
  "TPQA advisory": "TPQA 顾问",
  "CQC advisory": "CQC 顾问",
