  /* ---- home: FAQ ---- */
  "Important answers": "重要解答",
  "Frequent enquiries.": "常见咨询。",
  "The questions most often put to the practice, answered plainly.": "最常向本所提出的问题，如实作答。",
  "Why are your fees lower?": "为何贵所的收费较低？",
  "The difference reflects our overheads rather than any compromise in the work. We maintain no staffed office, carry no marketing costs to recover, and take no placement margin on the SMEs we source. Our fees account for the work itself and the people who carry it out, and we are happy to set out that basis for you in detail.":
    "其中的差别源于我们的间接成本，而非在工作上有任何妥协。我们不设专人办公室，无须摊销营销开支，亦不在所引荐的领域专家身上抽取中介利润。我们的费用只反映工作本身及执行工作的人，我们也乐意为您详细说明这一计算基础。",
  "May we apply your accreditations to work prepared elsewhere?": "我们可否将贵所的认证用于由他方完成的工作？",
  "We are not able to do so. Our accreditations attach only to work we have prepared ourselves, and to extend them to courseware authored by another would misrepresent that material to SSG and would not hold up on review. Where you have capable people of your own, we would be glad to work alongside them; what we cannot do is certify work we have not undertaken.":
    "恕难从命。我们的认证只附于由本所亲自完成的工作；若将其延伸至他方撰写的课件，便会向 SSG 作出失实陈述，亦无法通过审核。倘若贵机构自有能干的人手，我们乐意与其携手共事；但我们不能为并非由本所承办的工作背书。",
  "Who carries out the work?": "工作由谁执行？",
  "Each engagement is led by a Level 3 Senior Professional Adult Educator under TAEPP, supported by two curriculum developers accredited under DACE / DDDLP, and by three where the engagement calls for it. We do not subcontract, and we are glad to introduce you to the people who will be handling your matter.":
    "每一项委托均由一位 TAEPP 第三级资深专业成人教育工作者主理，并由两位经 DACE / DDDLP 认证的课程开发者协助；视委托需要可增至三位。我们不转包工作，并乐意向您引荐将经手您事务的人员。",
  "What does the first consultation involve?": "首次咨询包含哪些内容？",
  "It is a short conversation, around twenty minutes by call or by note, to understand the engagement, its timeline and the form of SSG funding that suits the course. We will give you a candid view of whether it is a matter we should take on and what it is likely to cost. There is no charge and no obligation on either side.":
    "这是一次简短的交流，约二十分钟，以通话或文字进行，旨在了解委托内容、时间安排，以及适合该课程的 SSG 资助形式。我们会坦诚地告知，这是否属于我们应当承接的事务，以及预计的费用。双方均无须付费，亦无任何义务。",

